item.title: Postgres.app 2.5.6
item.description:
February 2022 Bugfix Release

This update no longer includes PostgreSQL 9.5 or 9.6 since they are no longer supported.

Do not install this update if you are still using PostgreSQL 9.5 or 9.6.

If you are still using PostgreSQL 9.5 or 9.6, please migrate your database to a newer version before installing this upgrade.

  • PostgreSQL 10.20 with PostGIS 2.4.9
  • PostgreSQL 11.15 with PostGIS 2.5.5
  • PostgreSQL 12.10 with PostGIS 3.0.5
  • PostgreSQL 13.6 with PostGIS 3.1.5
  • PostgreSQL 14.2 with PostGIS 3.1.5
